claim.claim-text:
1. A sensor device, comprising:
a carrier element;
a structural element situated on the carrier element;
a housing, wherein the structural element and the carrier element are situated at least partially within the housing, and wherein the housing is a molded housing; and
an intermediate housing situated essentially between the housing and the structural element, wherein the intermediate housing is a premold housing defining an enclosed cavity in which the structural element is situated;
wherein the intermediate housing includes a first housing region and a second housing region configured to be connected to each other.
